metadata.name: Lady Unfreedom
metadata.description:
Lady Unfreedom - the digital Idol.
The clothes cover the entire body of the character, except for the head, hands and feet, which she stands on the broken shackles. The woman’s head is crowned with a crown consisting of a base and seven rays. In her right hand, raised above her head, she holds a
torch, in her left hand, bent at the elbow so that the brush is below the level of the shoulder a tablet. The seven rays on the statue’s crown symbolize the seven seas and
seven continents.
